text: DNIC can stand for: * Dirección Nacional de Inteligencia Criminal * Data Network Identification Code * Diffuse noxious inhibitory controls * In Christianity, Dominus Noster Iesus Christus (and other grammatical variants; "Our Lord Jesus Christ") * In biochemistry, dinitrosyl iron complex * Direcção nacional de investigação criminal (Angola) * DoD Network Information Center pt:Polícia Nacional (Angola)#Órgãos centrais
title: DNIC
